{"tid":1103297,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩倡「自力更生」向制裁國還擊","createTime":"2019-04-12T10:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T10:26:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8cf6cf046b3b4c18cafbbb64a140afbf01b296","tid":1103297,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190412/20654320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20654320&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8KjakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=95067ce5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20654320&h=72d4c6b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190412/20654320</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金正恩倡「自力更生」向制裁國還擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190412/large/a1903a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190412%2Flarge%2Fa1903a.gif&h=964b1f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正恩<br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩稱國家的社會主義經濟要「自力更生」，「對誤以為制裁可使朝鮮跪低的敵國施以沉重打擊，貫徹落實黨的新戰略路線」。這是他自美朝峯會破局後首次正式發言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對華府展示強硬姿態<br />\n<br />\n官媒朝中社昨日報道指，金正恩出席會議談到北韓的立場，指他會加倍努力構建一個自給自足的國家經濟。官媒刊登了金正恩上周五日內巡視至少四個經濟計劃的圖片和報道，包括到過一個改建了的百貨店、旅遊度假村及鄰近朝中邊境的經濟區。<br />\n<br />\n另外，消息人士指在特金會破局後，勞動黨內部下「封口令」，禁止任何人提起河內會談，「為了防止會談失敗的消息傳到朝鮮人民的耳中」，意味當局擔心金正恩面子受損打擊形象。<br />\n<br />\n而在朝中社的報道，正值美國總統特朗普與南韓總統文在寅昨日在華盛頓會面討論北韓等議題。美國國務卿蓬佩奧日前表示華府將維持施壓，直至北韓達至「全面可驗證的無核化」。分析指雖金正恩無點名指明「敵國」亦無提及核武，但已對華府展示出更為強硬的姿態。他所提及的戰略亦未知是指向發展經濟或是核武。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社/南韓《中央日報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n南韓裁定禁墮胎違憲 明年修法<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n澳洲下月大選 總理莫里森難冧莊"},{"pid":"fc3f38cea170bfe1b0721fa5039fbaa754ae2741","tid":1103297,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"自煮燃發"},{"pid":"eb35d9a971a56137dcfc08f0f0bdf8f5c962147b","tid":1103297,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"㓕左條肥仔啦，一條友害左幾千萬人"},{"pid":"1fa669e44139d33b0528c3111a632664b2e399d0","tid":1103297,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"想學古巴"},{"pid":"1eda2ab01a2956dfe6e3cda121ec85798178ca26","tid":1103297,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"之前唔係fd左咩<br />\n條肥仔又做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e23083ae242fe59e4073746bc11de1e677d79d","tid":1103297,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"佢只不過係中國只棋子姐"},{"pid":"85ceafb9015540a32d6f480bd42d9c306a33e214","tid":1103297,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"冇錢自力更生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n契哥刁近平都冇晒錢"},{"pid":"b5aa6a9530ffab3aa897b20cca5c7864bc7ab727","tid":1103297,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"由打J大始"}]}